nodes.text: Wedding of Wicket Wystri Warrick and Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka
The Wedding of Wicket Wystri Warrick and Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka took place sometime after the Battle of Endor, shortly after the death of Chief Chirpa.
The ceremony doubled as Kneesaa's induction as the new chief of Bright Tree Village.

In 1995, The Essential Guide to Characters hinted that Wicket would replace Chirpa as chief of Bright Tree Village. But the 2001 The Essential Guide to Alien Species indicated that Kneesaa became the new ruler (as it was originally implied she would be in Ewoks 2). However, Wicket's databank entry confirms that the couple co-ruled the village together, although it does not specify if Wicket was inducted at the same time as Kneesaa.
